Crude mortality and loss of life expectancy of patients diagnosed with 
urothelial carcinoma of the urinary bladder in Norway.

Andreassen BK(1), Myklebust TÅ(2), Haug ES(3)(4).

Author information:
(1)a Department of Research, Cancer Registry of Norway , Institute for 
Population-Based Research , Oslo , Norway.
(2)b Department of Registration, Cancer Registry of Norway , Institute for 
Population-Based Research , Oslo , Norway.
(3)c Vestfold Hospital Trust , Tønsberg , Norway.
(4)d Institute of Cancer Genetics and Informatics (ICI) , Oslo University 
